cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CV

The paper deals with the challenges of treating emoji as a new modality in multimedia research, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the prediction of emoji from text and images, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) respectively. The paper also presents results for multimedia retrieval using emoji as queries, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
